  "detailed_description": "Please wishlist to get news in the future!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602490/extras/8f6bb4b194011e36fb1e3208da0503c9.poster.avif?t=1726100240\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602490/extras/8f6bb4b194011e36fb1e3208da0503c9.webm?t=1726100240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602490/extras/8f6bb4b194011e36fb1e3208da0503c9.mp4?t=1726100240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You wake up one day and receive a letter from the head of the village \"Obihiro '' inviting you to save their village from threat. Deciding to set out on a journey to explore the world, defeat monsters, rescue Waifus and save the village.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Exciting rhythm-based combat with enemy and bosses<br></li><li>Exciting combination of rock metal, techno and retro music<br></li><li>Funny and smart sokoban-style puzzle<br></li><li>Animated enemies and cute chibi character<br></li><li>Beautiful background and environment<br></li><li>Large open region and many dungeon to explore</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602490/extras/db0bf3db8366bf1b9c03d14a7fc08dbb.poster.avif?t=1726100240\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602490/extras/db0bf3db8366bf1b9c03d14a7fc08dbb.webm?t=1726100240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602490/extras/db0bf3db8366bf1b9c03d14a7fc08dbb.mp4?t=1726100240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
